snippet.title: Alif Laila Full Story Cartoons in Urdu / Hindi
snippet.description:
Hello Friends,
I have brought back these  amazing episodes of old folk tales which have been obsoleted. Not at all inappropriate and every story have a moral for children and stories are displayed in such a way that kids won't be get bored. It is great for kids to understand the meaning of stories. These are so interesting and teaches values too. Every story teaches a moral lesson which is much needed now a days.
It was really beautiful and amazing show, I still watch this with complete interest even after being an adult.
